<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Error 404 (Not Found)</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 40px;
    }

    .error-message h1 {
        font-size: 100px;
        color: #ff6f61;
    }

    .error-message h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .error-message p {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #777;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .search-bar {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .search-bar input {
        padding: 10px;
        width: 80%;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .search-bar button {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ff6f61;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .buttons a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        margin: 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        background-color: #ff6f61;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .buttons a:hover {
        background-color: #ff3b3b;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-message">
            <h1>404</h1>
            <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
            <p>We can't seem to find the page you're looking for.</p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="back-btn">Go Back</a>
                <a href="/" class="home-btn">Go to Homepage</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>